"title": "6021: sin, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6021: sin, nature of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture portrays sin in terms of wrongness before God in a variety of different ways, such as uncleanness, guilt or rebellion.</p>\n<h2>The basic nature of sin</h2>\n<h3>All sin is directed against God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:4\">PSA 51:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:13\">GEN 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:16\">EXO 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:10\">JDG 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:4\">PSA 41:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:18\">LUK 15:18</a></p>\n<h3>Sin is essentially a lack of faith in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:23\">ROM 14:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></p>\n<h2>Descriptions of sin</h2>\n<h3>Corruption of God's good purposes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:5\">DEU 32:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:11-Gen6:12\">GEN 6:11–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:12\">DEU 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:29\">DEU 31:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:19\">JDG 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Doing evil in God's sight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19-John3:20\">JHN 3:19–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:11\">JDG 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:12-Ps34:16\">PSA 34:12–34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:13\">PRO 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:6-Isa59:7\">ISA 59:6–59:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:35\">MAT 12:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:45\">LUK 6:45</a></p>\n<h3>Ungodliness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:14-Jude1:15\">JUD 1:14–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:17\">ISA 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:6\">ISA 32:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:9\">1TI 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Rebellion against God's authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:9\">ISA 30:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:7\">DEU 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:23\">1SA 15:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:40\">PSA 78:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:56\">PSA 78:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:13\">JER 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:13\">HOS 7:13</a></p>\n<h3>The breaking or transgression of God's laws</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:4\">1JN 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:13-1Sam13:14\">1SA 13:13–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13\">1CH 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:29\">NEH 9:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:5\">MIC 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18\">MIC 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:23\">ROM 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:15\">ROM 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:14-Rom5:17\">ROM 5:14–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:10-Jas2:11\">JAS 2:10–2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Straying from the right path</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:6\">ISA 53:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:3\">PSA 58:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:10\">PSA 95:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:10\">PSA 119:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:21\">PSA 119:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:118\">PSA 119:118</a></p>\n<h3>Incurring a debt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:12\">MAT 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:21-Matt18:35\">MAT 18:21–18:35</a></p>\n<h3>Falling short of a standard</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a></strong> <em>The words most commonly used for “sin” in the OT and NT originally signified “missing the mark”.</em></p>\n<h3>Uncleanness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:2\">PSA 51:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:16\">ISA 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:7\">PSA 51:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of sin</h2>\n<h3>Sins of omission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:17\">JAS 4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:45\">MAT 25:45</a></p>\n<h3>Deliberate sins</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:47\">LUK 12:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:30-Num15:31\">NUM 15:30–15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:42-Deut1:43\">DEU 1:42–1:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:12\">DEU 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:13\">PSA 19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:17\">ISA 57:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:32\">ROM 1:32</a></p>\n<h3>Unintentional sins</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:48\">LUK 12:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev4:1-Lev4:5\">LEV 4:1–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:22-Num15:29\">NUM 15:22–15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:41-Deut4:42\">DEU 4:41–4:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:17\">ACT 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:13\">1TI 1:13</a></p>\n<h3>Sin against the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:29-Mark3:30\">MRK 3:29–3:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:31-Matt12:32\">MAT 12:31–12:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:10\">LUK 12:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:16\">1JN 5:16</a></p>",
